"      </a>",
"      <br/>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_basics\" href=\"UTD.htm?14/4/14402?source=see_link\">",
"       Patient information: Acute myeloid leukemia (AML) (The Basics)",
"      </a>",
"      <br/>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_basics\" href=\"UTD.htm?2/47/2802?source=see_link\">",
