"      </a>",
"     </p>",
"     <p>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"UTD.htm?34/4/34886?source=see_link\">",
"       Patient information: Bone marrow transplantation (stem cell transplantation) (Beyond the Basics)",
"      </a>",
"     </p>",
