"      </strong>",
"      View of the esophagus after endoscopic resection of the lesion in two pieces.",
"      <br>",
"       <strong>",
"        (D)",
"       </strong>",
"       Histopathological evaluation of the specimens showed a radically resected adenocarcinoma infiltrating the muscularis mucosae (T1m3).",
"       <br>",
